H0.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to the Army's Major. Lieutenant Commander

H1.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to the Army's Major. Commander

H2.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to the Army's Major. Captain

H3.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to the Army's Major. RADM

A4.text: Formerly equivalent to the Army rank of major, a commander is now equivalent in rank to a lieutenant colonel in the British Army.
